  ('medical-tech-moex-00513', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關紅血球之生理代謝，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["經由粒線體進行糖解作用產生能量", "經G6PD（glucose-6-phosphate dehydrogenase）之作用產生NADP以穩定血色素", "2,3-DPG（2,3-diphosphoglycerate）濃度上升時可提升血色素與氧之結合力", "Pyruvate kinase缺乏會造成慢性溶血"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00514', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關G6PD缺乏症的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["為紅血球的糖解途徑Embden-Meyerhof pathway的缺陷", "是一種患者男多於女的先天代謝異常疾病", "G6PD缺失影響紅血球內NADPH的唯一來源", "影響氧化態glutathione的還原作用，無法提供紅血球對抗氧化壓力"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00515', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關血管內溶血性貧血（intravascular hemolytic anemia）可能出現的現象，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["因溶血釋出的hemoglobin增多，導致血清haptoglobin濃度上升", "因紅血球破壞增加，骨髓代償性造血增加，導致reticulocyte count上升", "溶血釋出的hemoglobin上升，使透過尿液排除的urobilinogen濃度升高", "紅血球破壞增加，使血清中的lactate dehydrogenase濃度上升"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00516', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '正常成人血液中的血色素種類，依其含量由高至低排列，下列何者正確？', '["Hb A＞Hb A ＞Hb F 2", "Hb A＞Hb F＞Hb A 2", "Hb A ＞Hb A＞Hb F 2", "Hb F＞Hb A＞Hb A 2"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
